## Senior Software Engineer -- Acme Corporation (Mar 2022 -- Present)

**Team:** Platform Engineering, 8 engineers
**Tech:** Python, FastAPI, TypeScript, React, PostgreSQL, AWS, Kafka, Redis, Terraform

Key responsibilities and achievements:

- Led the migration of the monolithic payment service to microservices architecture
  - Reduced p99 latency from 800ms to 480ms on 2M+ daily transactions
  - Zero downtime cutover using strangler-fig pattern over 6 months
- Designed and built the real-time fraud detection pipeline
  - Kafka consumer processing 50K events/sec, Redis for real-time feature lookups
  - Cut false-positive rate from 12% to 7.8%, saving $400K/year in manual review costs
- Shipped a GraphQL + REST hybrid API used by 150+ enterprise clients
  - Owned API versioning strategy and backwards-compatibility guarantees
  - P99 < 120ms at peak load (30K req/s)
- Ran weekly code reviews and architecture discussions for junior engineers (3 reports)
- Introduced contract testing (Pact) across 12 microservices, catching 4 production regressions pre-release

