## Software Engineer -- Beta Startup (Jun 2019 -- Feb 2022)

**Team:** ML Platform, 5 engineers
**Tech:** Python, FastAPI, Airflow, dbt, PostgreSQL, AWS SageMaker, Docker, Kubernetes

Key responsibilities and achievements:

- Built the ML inference engine from scratch -- served 500K predictions/day at 99.9% uptime
  - FastAPI + Celery + Redis; horizontally scaled on EKS
  - Introduced model quantisation (INT8) -- reduced inference cost by 60%
  - Added batched inference -- increased throughput 8x at same hardware cost
- Designed and maintained the data ingestion pipeline processing 10TB/day
  - Airflow DAGs pulling from 20+ data sources (REST APIs, S3, Snowflake, Kafka)
  - dbt models for data transformation with 97% test coverage
- Owned the A/B testing framework used by 5 product teams
  - Enabled statistical significance calculations with Bayesian + frequentist modes
- Mentored 2 data science interns; both converted to full-time roles
